            "id": "20250416A05YWH",
            "title": "金饰品克价破千元关口 还买么？ |  XIN消费",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"><section><section style=\"outline:0px;text-align:left;visibility:visible\"><section><section><section style=\"line-height:1.75em;outline:0px;text-align:center;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><section style=\"line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;text-align:left;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"line-height:normal;outline:0px;text-align:center;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><h1 style=\"line-height:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;text-align:left\"><strong style=\"line-height:1.73em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;z-index:0;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"border-color:rgb(255, 0, 0);border-style:initial;border-width:0px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:20px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"margin-bottom:-13px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"margin:20px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"background-color:rgba(35, 168, 217, 0.1);font-size:15px;outline:0px;padding:15px;text-align:left;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O6Usq8rXBlGGSzblYtoVgZfofJyQWZIVu0Q1VVAXccPikAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/O6Usq8rXBlGGSzblYtoVgZfofJyQWZIVu0Q1VVAXccPikAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89)\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.73em;outline:0px;text-align:left;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"line-height:1.73em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:normal\">4月16日，国际金价再创新高。受此影响，国内实物黄金价格也随之上涨。当日，国内各金饰品品牌金价纷纷突破1000元/克大关，最高达1006元/克。</span></strong></strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></strong><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"line-height:2em;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127)\">记者</span></strong></strong><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127)\">｜张鑫  <br/></span></strong></strong></span></section><section style=\"line-height:2em;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127);display:none;line-height:0px\">‍‍‍</span></strong></strong></span></section><section style=\"line-height:2em;margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size:14px\">  编辑<strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span>｜余美</span></strong></strong><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;text-align:right;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span>  </span></strong></strong></span></strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127)\">实</span></strong><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.034em;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><span style=\"color:rgb(127, 127, 127)\">习生｜隋鑫</span></strong></span></section></section></section></section></strong></h1></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"text-align:center\"><section style=\"outline:0px;text-align:left;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"line-height:1.75em;outline:0px;text-align:center;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><section style=\"line-height:1.6em;outline:0px;text-align:left;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"line-height:normal;outline:0px;text-align:center;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><h1 style=\"line-height:normal;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px\"><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"margin-left:10px;margin-right:10px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><section style=\"color:rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size:16px\"><section style=\"line-height:0;margin-top:10px;text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" style=\"border-radius:6px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:unset;text-indent:0em;vertical-align:middle;width:139px;height:100%\"/></section></section></section></section></strong><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all !important\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(35, 168, 217);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration:none\">直播间代拆盲盒</span></strong></strong></h1></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"line-height:2em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">4月16日，国际金价再创新高。截至北京青年报记者发稿时，现货黄金报3279.53美元/盎司，涨幅1.74%。COMEX黄金期货报3293.2美元/盎司，涨幅1.63%，距3300美元关口仅一步之遥。受此影响，国内品牌金饰克价也随之上涨，多个品牌突破1000元大关。</span></section><p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OxQCH_ioDZ7_BTdhEUfsjp_4ejFOq9Bo_XEJ8LvuT7AEQAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/OxQCH_ioDZ7_BTdhEUfsjp_4ejFOq9Bo_XEJ8LvuT7AEQAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p style=\"line-height:2em;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">其中，<!-- -->周大福<!-- -->、六福、<!-- -->周大生<!-- -->等品牌饰品金价报1006元/克。老庙黄金、<!-- -->周生生<!-- -->报1003元/克。世界黄金协会最新研究显示，2025年第一季度实物支持的黄金交易所交易基金（ETF）流入量达到226吨，价值210亿美元，创下近三年来最大季度流入量。报告显示，北美上市基金占总流入资金的61%，欧洲市场占需求的22%左右，亚洲市场占全球流入资金的16%。</span></p><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\"><section style=\"text-align:center\"><section style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center\"><section style=\"font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"margin-top:16px\"><section style=\"display:inline-block;width:139px\"><section style=\"width:139px\"><section style=\"line-height:0;text-align:justify;width:139px\"><section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);display:inline-block;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:0;outline:0px;text-align:unset;vertical-align:baseline;visibility:visible;width:139px;word-break:break-all\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" style=\"border-radius:6px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:unset;text-indent:0em;vertical-align:middle;width:139px;height:100%\"/></section></section></section></section><section style=\"display:contents\"><section style=\"display:contents\"><section style=\"display:contents;text-align:unset\"><br style=\"outline:0px\"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(35, 168, 217);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration:none\">机构上调金价展望</span></strong></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height:2em;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\"></span><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">机构纷纷大幅上调黄金的价格展望。花旗研究金价可能在年底前攀升至3500美元。“在我们看来，金价将在年底前触及3500美元/盎司，因担心美国硬着陆/滞胀，对冲/投资需求大幅增加，这将支撑金价。”花旗称。</span></p></section><section style=\"margin-bottom:0px;text-align:center\"><section style=\"margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);outline:0px;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"outline:0px;text-align:left\"><section style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);outline:0px;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"background-color:rgb(254, 255, 255);outline:0px;visibility:visible\"><section style=\"margin:17px auto 6px;z-index:0\"><section style=\"line-height:2em;list-style:none;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all;zoom:1\"><section style=\"margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0pt;margin-right:0pt\"><section style=\"line-height:2em;padding:0pt;word-break:break-all\"><section><section style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing:0.544px\"><section style=\"font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:1.5em;outline:0px;text-align:center;visibility:visible\"><section><section style=\"display:inline-block;width:139px\"><section style=\"width:139px\"><section style=\"line-height:0;text-align:justify;width:139px\"><section style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);display:inline-block;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:0;outline:0px;text-align:unset;vertical-align:baseline;visibility:visible;width:139px;word-break:break-all\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" style=\"border-radius:6px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:unset;text-indent:0em;vertical-align:middle;width:139px;height:100%\"/></section></section></section></section><section style=\"display:contents\"><section style=\"display:contents\"><section style=\"display:contents\"><section style=\"display:contents;text-align:unset\"><br style=\"outline:0px\"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><p style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-top:0px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><strong><span style=\"color:rgb(35, 168, 217);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px;text-decoration:none\">关联美元避险能力</span></strong></p></section></section><p style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:2em;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\"></span><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">摩根大通<!-- -->的分析师亦关注4000美元的价格是否有可能实现。该行的研究人员指出，黄金价格从2500美元涨至3000美元仅用了210天，远快于此前平均超过1700天的500美元涨幅。</span><span style=\"font-size:var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing:0.034em;text-align:center;text-indent:0em\"></span></p><p style=\"background-color:rgb(254, 255, 255);caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:2em;list-style:none;margin:17px auto 6px;outline:0px;padding:0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all;z-index:0;zoom:1\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">另据业内人士预测，黄金疯涨的背后，其实意味着美元的避险能力在逐步下降。美国反复无常的政策行动正在侵蚀全球市场对美元的信任，金价的大幅上涨正是这种不确定性的体现。</span></p><p style=\"line-height:2em;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#595959\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px\">                  </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:unset\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/news_bt/GLukzYoqoS5wyCEQKM89AGSFCkiGHSw-tcpwji62PgyAgAA/0\" style=\"border-radius:6px;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family:微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:unset;text-indent:0em;vertical-align:middle;width:139px;height:100%\"/></span><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\"></span></p><section style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:2em;margin-top:0px;text-align:center\"><strong style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;text-indent:0em\"><span style=\"color:rgb(35, 168, 217);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">看好与警惕并存</span></strong></section><section style=\"background-color:rgb(254, 255, 255);caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;outline:0px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><section style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;line-height:1.33em;margin-bottom:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;visibility:visible;word-break:break-all\"><p style=\"line-height:2em;margin-top:16px;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\"></span><span style=\"color:rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size:16px;letter-spacing:1px\">展望后市，多位基金经理表达了对黄金长期配置价值的看好。不过，也有分析师提示投资者应保持警惕。法兴银行高级大宗商品策略师大卫·威尔逊表示，“黄金市场将消化或正常化。如果贸易紧张局势没有持续升级，金价将难以在下半年保持进一步的上行势头。”</span><span style=\"font-size:var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing:0.578px;text-align:center;text-indent:0em\"></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></div>",
